    user_response: "Apply the \"Technical Dashboard / Data Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Technical Dashboard / Data Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\\\"en\\\"><head><meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\"><script src=\\\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\\\"></script><link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Geist:wght@400;700&display=swap\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\"><style>body { font-family: \'Inter\', sans-serif; background-color: #0C0F14; color: #E2E8F0; margin: 0; overflow: hidden; }.font-display { font-family: \'Geist\', sans-serif; }.glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); border-radius: 1.25rem; }.sidebar-item { transition: all 0.2s ease; }.sidebar-item.active { background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1); border-left: 3px solid #4ADE80; color: #4ADE80; }.card-gradient { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2) 0%, rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1) 100%); }.glow-green { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2); }.status-pulse { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4ADE80; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }@keyframes pulse { 0% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.7; } 70% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.7; } }</style></head><body><div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] overflow-hidden\\\"><aside class=\\\"w-64 border-r border-white/5 bg-black/20 p-6 flex flex-col\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-10\\\"><div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4ADE80] to-[#3B82F6] flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-black\\\">S</div><span class=\\\"font-display font-bold text-xl tracking-tight uppercase\\\">SIPESAT</span></div><nav class=\\\"flex-1 space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"sidebar-item active px-4 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z\\\"/></svg><span class=\\\"font-medium\\\">Dashboard</span></div><div class=\\\"sidebar-item px-4 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-3 text-white/50 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z\\\"/></svg><span>AI Evaluation</span></div><div class=\\\"sidebar-item px-4 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-3 text-white/50 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10\\\"/></svg><span>Bin Status</span></div><div class=\\\"sidebar-item px-4 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-3 text-white/50 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\\\"/></svg><span>Rewards</span></div></nav><div class=\\\"mt-auto p-4 glass card-gradient\\\"><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/40 mb-2\\\">ECO FOOTPRINT</p><div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full bg-black/40 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#4ADE80] w-3/4\\\"></div></div><p class=\\\"text-[10px] mt-2 text-white/70\\\">You saved 4.2kg of plastic today</p></div></aside><main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col p-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0C0F14] to-[#050608]\\\"><header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-8\\\"><div><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-1\\\">Halo, Alex!</h1><p class=\\\"text-white/40 text-sm\\\">Selamat pagi, Ecosystem Guardian.</p></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"text-right\\\"><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Last Sync</p><p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#4ADE80] flex items-center gap-1 justify-end\\\"><span class=\\\"status-pulse\\\"></span> Real-time active</p></div><div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\\\"><img src=\\\"https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=Alex\\\" alt=\\\"Avatar\\\" class=\\\"w-full h-full\\\"></div></div></header><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"col-span-8 glass p-6 card-gradient flex justify-between items-center\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\"><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/50 uppercase tracking-widest font-medium\\\">Total Balance</p><h2 class=\\\"text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white\\\">Rp 245.500</h2><p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#4ADE80] font-medium\\\">+12.4% from last week</p></div><button class=\\\"h-32 w-32 glass bg-[#FACC15]/20 border-[#FACC15]/40 hover:bg-[#FACC15]/30 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 group transition-all\\\"><div class=\\\"p-3 bg-[#FACC15] rounded-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-8 h-8 text-black\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M12 4v1m6 11h2m-6 0h-2v4m0-11v3m0 0h.01M12 12h4.01M16 20h4M4 12h4m12 0h.01M5 8h2a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1H5a1 1 0 00-1 1v2a1 1 0 001 1zm12 0h2a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1h-2a1 1 0 00-1 1v2a1 1 0 001 1zM5 20h2a1 1 0 001-1v-2a1 1 0 00-1-1H5a1 1 0 00-1 1v2a1 1 0 001 1z\\\"/></svg></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#FACC15] uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">SCAN TO DISPOSE</span></button></div><div class=\\\"col-span-4 glass p-6 flex flex-col justify-between\\\"><div><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/50 uppercase tracking-widest font-medium mb-4\\\">System Health</p><div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center text-sm\\\"><span class=\\\"text-white/60\\\">Edge AI Core</span><span class=\\\"text-[#4ADE80] font-medium\\\">Optimal</span></div><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center text-sm\\\"><span class=\\\"text-white/60\\\">Bin Connectivity</span><span class=\\\"text-[#4ADE80] font-medium\\\">Stable</span></div><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center text-sm\\\"><span class=\\\"text-white/60\\\">Cloud API</span><span class=\\\"text-[#FACC15] font-medium\\\">Latency +12ms</span></div></div></div><div class=\\\"pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex-1 h-1 bg-[#4ADE80] rounded-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"flex-1 h-1 bg-[#4ADE80] rounded-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"flex-1 h-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full\\\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"glass p-4\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-2\\\">Plastic</p><p class=\\\"text-xl font-bold font-display text-white\\\">12.5 kg</p><div class=\\\"mt-2 w-full h-1 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-blue-500 w-1/2\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"glass p-4\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-2\\\">Metal</p><p class=\\\"text-xl font-bold font-display text-white\\\">8.2 kg</p><div class=\\\"mt-2 w-full h-1 bg-yellow-500/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-yellow-500 w-1/3\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"glass p-4\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-2\\\">Paper</p><p class=\\\"text-xl font-bold font-display text-white\\\">24.1 kg</p><div class=\\\"mt-2 w-full h-1 bg-green-500/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-green-500 w-3/4\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"glass p-4\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-2\\\">Organic</p><p class=\\\"text-xl font-bold font-display text-white\\\">15.0 kg</p><div class=\\\"mt-2 w-full h-1 bg-orange-500/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-orange-500 w-2/5\\\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\\\"flex-1 glass p-6 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-4\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-display font-bold\\\">Recent Transactions</h3><button class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#3B82F6] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\\\">View Full History</button></div><div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\"><table class=\\\"w-full text-sm text-left\\\"><thead class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase border-b border-white/5 font-display\\\"><tr class=\\\"text-left\\\"> <th class=\\\"pb-3\\\">Type</th><th class=\\\"pb-3\\\">Location</th><th class=\\\"pb-3\\\">Weight</th><th class=\\\"pb-3\\\">Amount</th><th class=\\\"pb-3\\\">Status</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\\\"text-white/70\\\"><tr class=\\\"border-b border-white/5\\\"><td class=\\\"py-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500\\\"></div> Plastic PET</td><td class=\\\"py-4\\\">Smart Bin #01 - Blok M</td><td class=\\\"py-4 font-display\\\">1.2 kg</td><td class=\\\"py-4 text-[#4ADE80] font-medium font-display\\\">+Rp 1.500</td><td class=\\\"py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] bg-white/5 text-white/40\\\">COMPLETED</span></td></tr><tr class=\\\"border-b border-white/5\\\"><td class=\\\"py-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500\\\"></div> Metal Can</td><td class=\\\"py-4\\\">Smart Bin #04 - Monas</td><td class=\\\"py-4 font-display\\\">0.5 kg</td><td class=\\\"py-4 text-[#4ADE80] font-medium font-display\\\">+Rp 2.200</td><td class=\\\"py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] bg-white/5 text-white/40\\\">COMPLETED</span></td></tr><tr class=\\\"\\\"><td class=\\\"py-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500\\\"></div> Mix Paper</td><td class=\\\"py-4\\\">Smart Bin #02 - Sudirman</td><td class=\\\"py-4 font-display\\\">2.8 kg</td><td class=\\\"py-4 text-[#4ADE80] font-medium font-display\\\">+Rp 800</td><td class=\\\"py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] bg-white/5 text-white/40\\\">COMPLETED</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></main></div></body></html>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Technical Dashboard / Data Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Technical Dashboard / Data Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\\\"en\\\"><head><meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\"><script src=\\\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\\\"></script><link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Geist:wght@400;700&display=swap\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\"><style>body { font-family: \'Inter\', sans-serif; background-color: #0C0F14; color: #E2E8F0; margin: 0; overflow: hidden; }.font-display { font-family: \'Geist\', sans-serif; }.glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); border-radius: 1.25rem; }.sidebar-item { transition: all 0.2s ease; }.sidebar-item.active { background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1); border-left: 3px solid #4ADE80; color: #4ADE80; }.card-gradient { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2) 0%, rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1) 100%); }.glow-green { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2); }.status-pulse { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4ADE80; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }@keyframes pulse { 0% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.7; } 70% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.7; } }</style></head><body><div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] overflow-hidden\\\"><aside class=\\\"w-64 border-r border-white/5 bg-black/20 p-6 flex flex-col\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-10\\\"><div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4ADE80] to-[#3B82F6] flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-black\\\">S</div><span class=\\\"font-display font-bold text-xl tracking-tight uppercase\\\">SIPESAT</span></div><nav class=\\\"flex-1 space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"sidebar-item active px-4 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z\\\"/></svg><span class=\\\"font-medium\\\">Dashboard</span></div><div class=\\\"sidebar-item px-4 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-3 text-white/50 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\\\"><svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" 