ble\", and \"Cloud API\" with \"+12ms\" latency. I\'m preparing to implement these edits.\n\n\n**Enhancing Transaction Display**\n\nI\'m now focused on the recent transactions list. I\'ve translated \"Recent Transactions\" to \"Transaksi Terakhir\" for improved localization. I\'m also preparing to enhance the display. I\'m confident in the approach to improve visual clarity.\n\n\n**Implementing Transaction Styling**\n\nI\'m now implementing the display details for each transaction in the \"Transaksi Terakhir\" list. I\'m focusing on the component that renders each transaction item, which will improve the visual presentation of the transactions. I\'m ensuring there is a clear visual distinction between each entry, and am incorporating hover effects. The design will show transaction type icons using `<TxIcon>` from the transaction\'s configuration, and I\'m ensuring the component utilizes a glass panel effect. I\'m confident that this approach will deliver a high-quality UI.\n\n\n**Refining Transaction Details**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the detailed display of each transaction within the list. I\'m incorporating the transaction date and time, formatting the amount with \'id-ID\' locale for rupiah, and applying styling to show the status. I\'m paying careful attention to text sizes, spacing, and use of primary colors to ensure a clean, understandable, and visually appealing presentation.\n\n\n**Implementing Transaction Styling**\n\nI\'m now integrating the right chevron icon for transaction list navigation, and also am adding a glass panel style to the transactions. I am also implementing the logic for hover effects to improve the user experience. The transactions will be styled to be visually clear and user-friendly.\n\n\n\n**Finalizing System Health Display**\n\nI\'m now focused on the final System Health display attributes. I\'m incorporating styling to show \"Edge AI Core\" as \"Optimal\" in green, \"Bin Connectivity\" as \"Stable\" in green, and \"Cloud API\" with \"+12ms\" latency in yellow. I\'m also adding a progress indicator to visualize overall health, to ensure a complete and informative display.\n\n\n\n"
